      <p class="call-breakout__sub prose" style="font-size:14.5px;color:var(--color-ink-mute);margin:0 auto 18px;max-width:64ch;">A Certified ProAdvisor (independent firm) reviews your own QuickBooks file free, then scopes the fix in writing within 3 business days &mdash; fixed-fee, never hourly. For Intuit account or billing issues, contact Intuit directly.</p>
      <a class="btn btn-cta" href="/quickbooks/file-review/?intent=file-review" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;height:48px;padding:0 22px;border-radius:11px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">Get the free file review</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

